com.cyc.base.kbtool

Interface LookupTool

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LookupToolImpl

    public interface LookupTool
    Tools for looking up CycObjects in the Cyc KB. To perform more complex inferences over the Cyc KB, use the InferenceTool.
    Author:
    nwinant
    See Also:

        CycList getAllDependentSpecs(Fort cycFort)
                      throws CycConnectionException,
                             CycApiException
        Gets the list of all of the dependent specs for a Fort collection. Dependent specs are those direct and indirect specs of the collection such that every path connecting the spec to a genl of the collection passes through the collection. In a typical taxomonmy it is expected that all-dependent-specs gives the same result as all-specs.

        Returns:
